## Theorem Existance of Laplace{}

:::{#thm-ExistLaplace}
## Existance of Laplace Transform

If $f(t)$ is `piecewise continuous` for $t\geq 0$ and `of exponential order` for some positive constant $C$ and for $t\geq T$, then $$\mathscr{L}\{f(t)\}$$ exists for $s>C$.

:::

